Reference: Shipley, Bill &amp; Vu, Thi-Tam. (2002). Dry matter content as a measure of dry matter concentration in plants and their parts. New Phytologist. 153. 359 - 364. 10.1046/j.0028-646X.2001.00320.x. </comment>
